
" Map to fast switch opened splits.
nnoremap <C-J> <C-W><C-J>
nnoremap <C-K> <C-W><C-K>
nnoremap <C-L> <C-W><C-L>
nnoremap <C-H> <C-W><C-H>

" Map to switch tabs forward by Control+Tab and backward by Control+Shit+Tab
map <C-Tab> gt
map <C-S-Tab> gT

" Setting vim automatically chosing current working directory to the same as the file you are editing.
set autochdir
